Možda ćemo te videti ponovo.

1250
01:19:23,330 --> 01:19:25,533
Niko zaista ne zna kako to deluje.

1251
01:20:55,289 --> 01:20:57,424
Gaa...

1252
01:20:57,458 --> 01:20:59,594
Gaa.

1253
01:21:20,214 --> 01:21:21,649
Hej.

1254
01:21:21,683 --> 01:21:23,183
Kod kuće si.

1255
01:21:24,519 --> 01:21:27,388
Bolesna si?

1256
01:21:27,421 --> 01:21:30,525
- Ne.
- Šta nije u redu?

1257
01:21:30,558 --> 01:21:33,293
Oh...

1258
01:21:33,327 --> 01:21:37,131
Samo sam malo umorna.

1259
01:21:37,164 --> 01:21:38,465
Počeću večeru.

1260
01:21:38,499 --> 01:21:41,669
U redu je. Ne moraš ništa da mi spremaš.

1261
01:21:41,703 --> 01:21:44,204
Nisam gladna.

1262
01:21:44,238 --> 01:21:46,508
Šta je sa svim tim kutijama?

1263
01:21:48,175 --> 01:21:49,314
To su samo neke stvari

1264
01:21:49,339 --> 01:21:52,179
koje ću odneti u prodavnicu polovne robe.

1265
01:21:52,212 --> 01:21:55,048
Htela sam da ih odvezem popodne.

1266
01:21:56,651 --> 01:21:58,452
Šta?

1267
01:21:58,485 --> 01:22:00,254
Ne.

1268
01:22:04,124 --> 01:22:06,493
Zašto bi to dala?

1269
01:22:08,095 --> 01:22:10,632
Mi nećemo imati više bebe.

1270
01:22:10,665 --> 01:22:13,167
Pa, nismo pričali o tom.

1271
01:22:13,200 --> 01:22:15,402
Ti... ti to ne znaš.

1272
01:22:15,436 --> 01:22:18,405
Ne, nećemo da pričamo o tom, Čarlse.

1273
01:22:21,108 --> 01:22:22,510
Gde je ostatak od ovog?

1274
01:22:26,681 --> 01:22:28,115
Dobro.

1275
01:22:47,501 --> 01:22:48,969
Nisi.

1276
01:22:51,773 --> 01:22:56,210
Alison, reci mi da nisi.

1277
01:22:56,243 --> 01:22:57,645
Nema više beba.

1278
01:23:01,683 --> 01:23:03,718
Imala sam podvezivanje jajnika.

1279
01:23:06,220 --> 01:23:08,288
Ne, ne.

1280
01:23:11,425 --> 01:23:13,595
Ne.

1281
01:23:13,628 --> 01:23:17,699
Zato što Alison,
da, sigurno,

1282
01:23:17,732 --> 01:23:20,200
ti bi pričala o tom sa mnom,
zar ne?

1283
01:24:14,421 --> 01:24:16,123
Da li si žališ?

1284
01:24:16,156 --> 01:24:19,359
Žalim, zašto?

1285
01:24:19,393 --> 01:24:22,362
Naš brak.

1286
01:24:22,396 --> 01:24:24,164
Naš zajednički život.

1287
01:24:29,369 --> 01:24:31,573
Čarlse, kako možeš da pitaš to?

1288
01:24:31,606 --> 01:24:33,608
Pa, nije bilo lako.

1289
01:24:33,641 --> 01:24:38,613
Mislim da ne možeš da žališ ni za čim
kad dobiješ dete.

1290
01:24:38,646 --> 01:24:40,882
Kako to misliš?

1291
01:24:40,915 --> 01:24:43,283
Mislim, sve što si radio do ovog trenutka.

1292
01:24:43,317 --> 01:24:45,485
Svako skretanje s pravog puta.

1293
01:24:45,520 --> 01:24:47,789
Svi izbori.

1294
01:24:49,524 --> 01:24:52,594
Sve je to dovelo do njih.

1295
01:24:52,627 --> 01:24:59,056
Tako da žaliti za bilo čim, poželeti da se
bilo šta od toga promeni ...

1296
01:25:00,702 --> 01:25:03,470
...dovelo bi do drugačijeg rezutata,
zar ne?

1297
01:25:12,914 --> 01:25:14,549
Moram da idem.

1298
01:25:14,582 --> 01:25:15,583
Izvini.

1299
01:25:15,617 --> 01:25:17,852
- Ne, u redu je.
- Dobro je. U redu je.

1300
01:25:17,885 --> 01:25:20,187
Hvala, ipak.

1301
01:25:20,220 --> 01:25:23,591
I uzeću kupon za to vino.

1302
01:25:23,625 --> 01:25:25,292
Čuvaj se.

1303
01:25:43,745 --> 01:25:45,345
Pobedio sam!

1304
01:25:45,379 --> 01:25:46,648
Vidi, Čarli.

1305
01:25:46,681 --> 01:25:48,950
Uradio sam to ponovo.

1306
01:25:48,983 --> 01:25:52,620
- Bravo, dečko, ja.
- Vidim, Dana.

1307
01:25:54,656 --> 01:25:56,858
Pokušaj ti, Čarli.

1308
01:25:56,891 --> 01:25:58,489
Ne, u redu je.

1309
01:25:58,514 --> 01:25:59,527
Pobedio si.

1310
01:25:59,560 --> 01:26:02,797
Radiću na ovom sada.

1311
01:26:02,830 --> 01:26:03,965
Šta je to?

1312
01:26:03,998 --> 01:26:05,533
Pokaži.

1313
01:26:05,566 --> 01:26:08,502
Znaš, možda kasnje...

1314
01:26:08,536 --> 01:26:10,571
Evo, možeš da uzmeš ovo nazad.

1315
01:26:10,605 --> 01:26:13,340
Pokazaću ti kad završim.

1316
01:26:13,373 --> 01:26:14,542
Dobro.

1317
01:26:14,575 --> 01:26:17,344
Pokaži mi kad završiš.

1318
01:26:20,682 --> 01:26:21,949
Peder.

1319
01:26:23,250 --> 01:26:24,284
Kvir.

1320
01:26:24,317 --> 01:26:25,520
Retard.

1321
01:26:31,258 --> 01:26:33,661
Ha, hm.

