1617
01:47:14,101 --> 01:47:16,871
Romi, ovo je...

1618
01:47:16,904 --> 01:47:19,807
- Kodijeva mama.
- Da.

1619
01:47:19,840 --> 01:47:21,793
Izvinite, treba da se vratim.

1620
01:47:21,818 --> 01:47:23,644
Vidimo se u ponedeljak,
gospodine Marlou.

1621
01:47:23,678 --> 01:47:26,881
- Kladi se. - Drago mi je da sam vas
upoznala, gospođo Marlou.

1622
01:47:26,914 --> 01:47:28,783
Oh, da, pa,

1623
01:47:28,816 --> 01:47:31,752
