U Kaliforniji.

1628
01:47:39,961 --> 01:47:41,028
Ah.

1629
01:47:44,098 --> 01:47:45,232
Hajde.

1630
01:47:48,002 --> 01:47:49,704
Prestani s tim.

1631
01:47:52,006 --> 01:47:53,574
Primamljivo je.

1632
01:48:02,717 --> 01:48:03,951
Oh.

1633
01:48:08,089 --> 01:48:09,857
Vau.

1634
01:48:12,793 --> 01:48:14,425
